readable.content: A person jumping high above their skateboard on the street . A skateboarder flies through the air . A young man is caught in midair while doing a skateboard trick in an urban environment . Skateboarder jumping in air and his skateboard is between his legs . The skateboard is falling away from the skateboarder as he attempt a jump .
